{"tid":1421173,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"經歷北角一戰，有感受，勇武請看看","createTime":"2019-08-06T07:15:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T08:05:00.000Z","uid":276209,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0d9b9dfcd3bb769f0de6fcaf9cfacb11d631385f","tid":1421173,"uid":276209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:15:05.000Z","msg":"首先大家休息嘅，休息；食飯要食餐好，好補充番體力同精神咁先可以繼續落去下一場。<br />\n<br />\n講返琴日，覺得係咁金鐘執催淚彈嘅效率好咗好多，特別要用蒸餾水樽+紙皮封好，幾乎冇煙的。要分開3-5人一組，分佈係煙霧彈落腳點，準備「收拾」煙霧彈，絕對有信心、有把握係短時間熄滅所有煙。<br />\n<br />\n跟住落北角，同福建幫打左一輪，發現gear真系好重要，以我地速度和組織力，真系可以擊退對手，但有用的gear幾乎可以令被打都唔會痛，可以擋好衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n最好，一定保命，走係為左回來再打、再來、再戰。"},{"pid":"eafe79a7694bc0a6a79515f37090a658949de461","tid":1421173,"uid":276209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:15:14.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"4c74f61df5a0e40e2a50b49b94ba95468d6d8b71","tid":1421173,"uid":276209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:15:26.000Z","msg":"Up again"},{"pid":"5e0677aa0778dcf8216b2158b486fc3db7afaa82","tid":1421173,"uid":276209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:16:19.000Z","msg":"Upup"},{"pid":"6afc6e8d1966501f7b9d5a2b6586578049c6dff7","tid":1421173,"uid":276209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:18:52.000Z","msg":"upup2"},{"pid":"f8f45b7f840cd87152dc1f6a9fae393d3e39e1b2","tid":1421173,"uid":276209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:20:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2fc612f746d3e02a6667b8cc4b92e8baef4de9e0","tid":1421173,"uid":276209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:21:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7fd061cc410f8d759d0ae38619b65b924a31ec60","tid":1421173,"uid":276209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:22:53.000Z","msg":"麻煩俾多d前線戰友知道"},{"pid":"8aa833ababcdb0c3e8a2012bb28f8794c012ad5e","tid":1421173,"uid":281029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d9b9dfcd3bb